            <div1>
                <pb facs="ccda.corr00214.001.jpg"/>

                <fw type="letterhead" place="top-left" hand="#h01">CHAS. W. CHESNUTT<lb/> 1105
                    WILLIAMSON BUILDING<lb/> CLEVELAND O</fw>


                <note type="authorial" hand="#h04"><hi rend="underline"><gap reason="illegible"/></hi></note>

                <dateline><date when="1915-12-29"><add hand="#h03">Dec. 29, 1915</add></date></dateline>

                <opener> <salute>Dear Friend Traubel:&#8212;<note type="editorial" resp="#slg" target="#Traub"/></salute> </opener>

                <p hand="#h03">The receipt of your Birthay Card, for which please accept my thanks,
                    reminds me that I owe you a dollar, which please find enclosed.</p>

                <closer> <salute>With the compliments of the season,</salute> <salute>Yours
                    sincerely,</salute> <signed hand="#h03">Chas. W. Chesnutt.</signed> </closer>

            </div1>

        </body>

